  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underquest </strong> is a fantasy roguelite adventure game with fast-paced combat and deep inventory management. Collect items and merge them into special skills. Explore randomly generated dungeons with various game encounters. Upgrade your hero with equipment and modifiers for creating diverse and powerful builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sort constantly refilled inventory<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The inventory will continuously be replenished, so dismantle it quickly. Combine items with each other, use obtained abilities in combat, or equip armor on your hero.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help characters in the tavern and improve yourself</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between your quests, you can meet other characters at the underground tavern. Find out about each character's story and they will reward you with special perks.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied combinations of items and skills in the inventory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 bosses with unique strategies, various enemies, and game events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 characters in the tavern with their own stories and perks to upgrade</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure story of underground clans and the mystery of the sealed surface</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underquest </strong> is a fantasy roguelite adventure game with fast-paced combat and deep inventory management. Collect items and merge them into special skills. Explore randomly generated dungeons with various game encounters. Upgrade your hero with equipment and modifiers for creating diverse and powerful builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sort constantly refilled inventory<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The inventory will continuously be replenished, so dismantle it quickly. Combine items with each other, use obtained abilities in combat, or equip armor on your hero.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help characters in the tavern and improve yourself</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between your quests, you can meet other characters at the underground tavern. Find out about each character's story and they will reward you with special perks.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied combinations of items and skills in the inventory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 bosses with unique strategies, various enemies, and game events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 characters in the tavern with their own stories and perks to upgrade</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure story of underground clans and the mystery of the sealed surface</p></li></ul>",
